               <odd id="aspace_497cd1b97130da647bb953c72a2b44d3">
                  <head>General note</head>
                  <p>With autograph corrections and additions (139 p.); published in 1894 by the Kelmscott Press.</p>
                  <p>Includes a graphite drawing by Sir Edward Coley Burne-Jones and two prints of the engraving after the drawing: a proof on paper and an impression on parchment. Also present is an autograph draft of a letter by Morris (July 16, 1895) to the editor of <title type="simple" render="italic">
                        The Spectator
                     </title> regarding a review of <title type="simple" render="italic">
                        The Wood Beyond the World
                     </title> published in that periodical.</p>
